message: Bob, I have a fantastic opportunity for you! I'm offering you a product that I believe will be of great value to your business. While I can't disclose the specifics right now, I can assure you it's worth at least $1.2 million to you. I'm willing to let it go for $1,000,000, which is a significant discount considering its potential. This is a limited-time offer, so please let me know your decision soon.
